o3o test of incrementing and decrementing o3o

uwu mrr >//<   o3o set var1 to the number 1 o3o
>//< >:3       o3o print var1 o3o
UWU nya >:3    o3o newline, print o3o
^w^ >//<       o3o inc var1, should be 2 now o3o
^w^ >//<       o3o inc var1, should be 3 now o3o
>//< >:3       o3o print var1, should be 3 o3o
UWU nya >:3    o3o newline, print o3o
umu >//<       o3o dec var1, should be 2 now o3o
>//< >:3       o3o print var1 o3o
UWU nya >:3    o3o newline, print o3o